data.description:
IMPROVED PRICE!! MOTIVATED SELLER!!

Explore the perfect home at Pine Grove Meadows! FRESHLY COATED WITH NEW INTERIOR PAINT AND CARPETS METICULOUSLY CLEANED,  this delightful residence is nestled in the sought-after vicinity of Staley High School. The fenced backyard is a retreat of tranquility, featuring a beautifully stained 20x10 deck and a 20x11 patio, creating an inviting ambiance for entertaining guests or basking in the warmth of a sunny summer day.

THE KITCHEN, BATHROOM, AND FRONT ENTRYWAY FLOORS HAVE RECEIVED A MAKEOVER, WITH THE HARDWOOD FLOORS THOUGHTFULLY REFINISHED. IN ADDITION, THE BATHROOM FLOORS AND SHOWER TILES HAVE BEEN CAREFULLY SEALED AND REJUVENATED, ENHANCING THEIR OVERALL APPEARANCE.

The kitchen has witnessed the creation of countless delicious meals and offers ample pantry space to house all your culinary essentials. The master bedroom is a sanctuary of comfort, boasting a ceiling fan, vaulted ceiling, an en suite bathroom, and two closets for your convenience.

The walkout basement is a versatile space, perfect for gatherings, complete with a half bath and ample room for watching the game while grilling on the patio. Just a short stroll away, you'll discover the community clubhouse, featuring a fitness center, pool, playground, and more.

If you desire a comfortable lifestyle in a prime location, look no further – this home is an exceptional choice, and the seller is a pleasure to work with!
